casebody.data:
O. John BENISEK, et al., appellants,
v.
Linda H. LAMONE, Administrator, Maryland State Board of Elections, et al. No. 17-333. Supreme Court of the United States Dec. 8, 2017.

Appeal from the United States District Court for the District of Maryland. Further consideration of the question of jurisdiction is postponed to the hearing of the case on the merits.
